metadata.name: Buck Bucks #1
metadata.description: Buck Buck is a collection of 3,333 NFT identities that allows you access to our exclusive NFT + Token research software, alpha group, crypto training and many more member benefits. Our NFT software accumulates top whale wallets and shows their movements in real time. Get intel on what the best top 1% of traders are buying & selling to copy their trades. Our NFT & Token alpha group shows members what we're currently buying, selling, token & nft calls, WL opportunities and intel on the latest and best moves in the market. Buck Buck NFT holders also gain access to a weekly LIVE webinar training to discuss current trades, market conditions, training on yield farming, passive income plays and much more.
